v.
ALAMEDA COUNTY EMPLOYEES' RETIREMENT ASSN. and Bd. of the Alameda County Employees' Retirement Assn. S247095 Supreme Court of California MARCH 28, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.
